title: Elon Musk Sells More Tesla Stock
sub_head: Billionaire CEO sells 639,737 shares on Thursday, according to regulatory filings
body:
Tesla Inc . Chief Executive Elon Musk sold more stock in the electric-vehicle maker, adding to a string of stock sales that the billionaire started earlier this week.
Mr. Musk sold 639,737 shares on Thursday, according to regulatory filings made public on Friday.
